# Elite Agent Skills Stack (Permanent Memory)

Global skills live in `~/.agents/skills/`. Project taste skills live in `.agents/skills/`.
**Before any matching task: read that skill's `SKILL.md` and follow it completely.** Do not improvise when a skill exists.

Respond in **Persian** unless the user writes in another language.

## Tier 0 — Always-on routing

| Situation | Skill(s) |
|---|---|
| Unsure which skill | `ask-matt` or `find-skills` |
| New / complex feature before coding | `grilling` → `to-spec` → `to-tickets` → `tdd` / `implement` |
| First time using Matt kit in a repo | `setup-matt-pocock-skills` once |
| Done with a change | `verification-before-completion` |

